    "For few-shot sizes 10 and 50-400, the best performing model alternates between the medbertde-base-domain and medbertde-base-comb PET models.",
    "Similar to gbert models, the relative gain of pretraining decreases with increasing shot sizes.",
    "It appears that our pretraining method using cardiovascular doctor's letters has no impact or may even impair the medbertde model.",
    "A possible reason could be that the public medbertde model was only pretrained on 10G of clinical and medical texts, primarily from the oncology domain.",
